[{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0004","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-32781","title":"Apollo Portal 配置中心未授权访问漏洞","description":"Apollo 配置中心 Portal 在 2.5.0 版本之前存在未授权访问漏洞。当目标环境启用了 configView.memberOnly.envs 配置时，低权限认证用户可直接向 /envs/{env}/releases/{releaseId} 接口发送请求，通过构造有效的 release ID 绕过权限校验，获取其未被授权的应用或命名空间的配置发布数据。该接口未调用 UserPermissionValidator.shouldHideConfigToCurrentUser 进行权限检查，导致敏感配置信息泄露。攻击者需拥有 Portal 的低权限账号并知晓目标 release ID，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.5,"aliases":["CVE-2025-32781","GHSA-jxpj-9j24-w337"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2026-07-12","updated":"2026-07-13","remediation":"升级 Apollo Portal 至 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复未授权访问问题。修复提交为 apolloconfig/apollo@362735d，对应 PR #5378。如无法立即升级，可启用 configView.memberOnly.envs 配置并严格限制环境访问权限，同时在网关或反向代理层对 GET /envs/{env}/releases/{releaseId} 接口添加额外的身份校验中间件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/security/advisories/GHSA-jxpj-9j24-w337","https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/pull/5378","https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/commit/362735ded4f13b62f6ab9df135d7096066e8e291","https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/releases/tag/v2.5.0"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0001","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-45422","title":"Proximus b-box 路由器 UPnP 访问控制不当漏洞","description":"Proximus b-box 路由器 UPnP 功能存在访问控制不当漏洞（CWE-284）。已获得路由器管理权限的攻击者可利用该缺陷绕过正常的访问限制机制，未经授权直接修改端口转发规则，导致内部网络服务被意外暴露至公网，增加被远程攻击的风险。该漏洞影响 Proximus b-box v8c.725A 版本，CVSS 评分 8.1，危害等级高。建议用户及时关注厂商固件更新以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-45422"],"sources":["cnnvd"],"published":"2026-07-09T21:16:54.167","updated":"2026-07-10T18:53:55.130","remediation":"建议立即登录 Proximus b-box 路由器管理后台（通常为 192.168.1.1），在「维护」或「系统」页面检查固件更新，将固件升级至 v8c.725A 及以后修复版本。如厂商尚未发布补丁，可在「高级设置」中关闭 UPnP 服务（取消勾选「启用 UPnP」），并限制管理界面仅允许内网 IP 地址访问，以防止攻击者从外部网络利用该漏洞修改端口转发规则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://b-box.com","http://proximus.com","https://github.com/Cedrico03/CVE-2025-45422---Bbox","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln-metrics/cvss/v3-calculator?vector=AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H/E:H/RL:U/RC:C/CR:H/IR:H/AR:H/MAV:N/MAC:L/MPR:N/MUI:N/MS:C/MC:H/MI:H/MA:H&version=3.1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0001.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0002","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-58151","title":"Xapi varstored 条件竞争漏洞","description":"varstored 是 Xapi 工具栈中处理虚拟机 UEFI 变量的核心组件，其与虚拟机内部的 OVMF 通过共享缓冲区进行通信。由于缺少足够的编译器内存屏障，共享缓冲区中的数据存在 TOCTOU（时间检查与使用时间）竞态条件漏洞，攻击者可通过提前修改共享缓冲区内容来操控跳转表中的索引，可能导致任意代码执行或信息泄露。该漏洞影响使用 Xapi 工具栈的虚拟化平台，CVSS 评分 9.4，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.4,"aliases":["CVE-2025-58151"],"sources":["cnnvd"],"published":"2026-07-09T16:16:33.817","updated":"2026-07-09T17:16:56.770","remediation":"升级 varstored 到包含 CVE-2025-58151 修复的版本，具体可通过更新 Xapi toolstack 至最新补丁版（关注 XenServer/XCP-ng 厂商安全公告）。如无法立即升级，可在 VM 配置中禁用 UEFI 启动并切换为 BIOS 模式作为临时缓解措施，或限制对受影响 VM 的管理操作并发数以降低竞争窗口命中概率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://xenbits.xen.org/xsa/advisory-478.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/01/27/2","http://xenbits.xen.org/xsa/advisory-478.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0005","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-46571","title":"Open WebUI 存储型跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Open WebUI（自托管AI平台）存在存储型跨站脚本（Stored XSS）漏洞，CWE-79分类。低权限用户可通过`/api/v1/files/`接口上传包含恶意JavaScript代码的HTML文件，服务器返回文件ID后，攻击者可构造链接诱导管理员点击，从而劫持管理员账户，进而利用管理员权限通过平台功能实现远程代码执行。默认配置下低权限用户上传的文件仅管理员或上传者自身可查看，限制了攻击面但未消除风险。该漏洞影响0.6.6之前版本，CVSS评分5.3，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.3,"aliases":["CVE-2025-46571","GHSA-8gh5-qqh8-hq3x"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2025-05-05T19:15:57.050","updated":"2026-06-17T09:26:38.630","remediation":"升级 Open WebUI 至 v0.6.6 及以上版本（官方已修复文件上传 XSS 漏洞）。如暂无法升级，可在反向代理层限制 `/api/v1/files/` 端点的上传文件类型，禁止上传 `.html` 后缀文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/blob/main/backend/open_webui/routers/files.py#L434-L438","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/commit/ef2aeb7c0eb976bac759e59ac359c94a5b8dc7e0","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/security/advisories/GHSA-8gh5-qqh8-hq3x"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0005.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0006","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-46719","title":"Open WebUI 存储型跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Open WebUI 是一个自托管的人工智能平台，在 0.6.6 版本之前存在存储型跨站脚本漏洞。攻击者可在聊天消息中插入未转义的 HTML 标签和恶意 JavaScript 代码，当其他用户打开包含恶意代码的聊天记录时，脚本会在受害者浏览器中执行，窃取访问令牌从而完全控制受害者账户。若受害者是管理员，攻击者可进一步创建恶意 Python 函数实现服务器端远程代码执行。此外，该漏洞可通过社区共享功能实现跨用户传播，危害范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-2025-46719","GHSA-9f4f-jv96-8766"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2025-05-05T19:15:57.197","updated":"2026-06-17T09:26:52.230","remediation":"立即升级 Open WebUI 至 v0.6.6 或以上版本，该版本已对 HTML 标签进行正确转义以防御 XSS。如无法立即升级，建议在管理面板中关闭「Enable Community Sharing」功能，并禁止用户分享聊天记录以降低攻击面。临时缓解措施还可配置 WAF 规则过滤聊天消息中的恶意 HTML/JavaScript 载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/blob/main/src/lib/components/chat/Messages/Markdown/MarkdownTokens.svelte#L269-L279","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/commit/6fd082d55ffaf6eb226efdeebc7155e3693d2d01","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/security/advisories/GHSA-9f4f-jv96-8766","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2025/CVE-2025-46719.md","https://github.com/Tencent/AI-Infra-Guard/blob/e00b340019f3b31282b4417e15c49f027f0909d3/data/vuln/openwebui/CVE-2025-46719.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/2025/46xxx/CVE-2025-46719.json","https://github.com/Tabll/gemnasium-db/blob/c78813392a686be9ed8245543249abb80331d014/pypi/open-webui/CVE-2025-46719.yml","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/90bd0a835ff7ed8cfea0a199ea9e2f05e33d6c81/2025/46xxx/CVE-2025-46719.json","https://github.com/sec-dojo-com/cve-poc/blob/b705b33e466c706c1129370e07ab2e4166c35b4c/pocs/2025/CVE-2025-46719.md","https://github.com/pypa/advisory-database/blob/3d0187a2ae2380c20a24da45e4f13e8bdd980484/vulns/open-webui/PYSEC-2026-2716.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/SSVC/data/2025/CVE-2025-46719.json","https://github.com/stevologic/security-recipes.ai/blob/f6129ff19f955337f9f194ea8d5a3937dce9acb8/content/recipes/cve/cve-2025-46719-open-webui-vulnerable-to-stored-xss-via-unescaped-markdown-token-in-markdowntokens-svelte-leading-to-full-acco.md","https://github.com/cyberdudebivash/cyberdudebivash-blog/blob/be80f241080dc6ff384600eeed4a5579a42f2524/api/intel/products/cve-2025-46719-pip-open-webui.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0006.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0006.toml"}]